EmoLib: Emotional Library
=========================

One line description:

	Library that tags incoming affective text


Attributions:

	Enginyeria i Arquitectura La Salle
	(Universitat Ramon Llull)
	http://www.salle.url.edu 


Development:

	EmoLib was originally developed by David Garcia
	as his Master's Thesis in Multimedia
	Engineering.

	Presently, EmoLib is being developed by
	Alexandre Trilla as part of his Ph.D. Thesis in
	Information Technologies.


